Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.52,0:00:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With an aura of calm determination,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.90,0:00:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rafael, one of the three Musketeers of Doma, was waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His battle spirit has told me just how strong of an opponent he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You say we are both comrades who are fighting against fate, Rafael?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.41,0:00:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I will not lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Justice that allows you to destroy this world... Such a thing does not exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.30,0:00:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometime ago, for the sake of living, we left behind our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.26,0:00:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We deceived ourselves, clinging to this mere illusion as we danced...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.56,0:01:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With closed eyes, at the end of the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was searching for your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.28,0:01:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We embrace our dreams and continue on...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.29,0:01:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within the swaying traces of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.22,0:01:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will once again grasp hold of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.31,0:01:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these feelings I have locked away in my heart... Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:02:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Truth about Doma"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never use The Barrier of Orichalcos in this Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.81,0:02:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this attack gets through, it will be vital damage to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead, Guardian Grarl!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Swift Cleave Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.55,0:02:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Special Ability of Kuribi is that it can make the opponent's Attack zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hence ending the Battle Phase for one turn only.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I've been underestimating your charming little servants.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have the feeling that both of them are on par at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Doma's got this "Barrier of Orichalcos" card...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thing is, when's the guy gonna activate the thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we cross up ahead, we'll reach Death Valley!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hang on, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This all right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing "all right" about this at all~!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:04:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard it from my grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Yugi has two different personalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The original Yugi, and the Yugi who holds the spirit of the nameless Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. The other Yugi is very dependable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's incredibly powerful when it comes to Dueling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.81,0:04:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I have no worries about him winning his match.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.77,0:04:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu, you like the Yugi who used to be King, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.03,0:04:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you saying that all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, we won't become love rivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because the one I like is the original Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.66,0:04:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I first met Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He purposely lost to me in our Duel in order to get an important message across.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darling is really very kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what the situation may be, he's always very considerate to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.68,0:04:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like you said, everything's going to be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:05:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"King" Yugi and Darling...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.11,0:05:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as the two work together, nobody can defeat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this moment, the magical effects of Purity of the Cemetery are activated!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have three Monsters in your Graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, you will be inflicted 300 points of damage to your Life Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.22,0:05:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The other me, please don't be anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We still have a chance against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah. I know, Partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.22,0:05:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Magic Card, Pot of Greed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can draw two cards from my deck
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The one card that can get me out of this predicament...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...is still asleep in my deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Kuriboh Brothers'\N Special Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Summon Kuribabylon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I use Kuribabylon as a sacrifice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Kuribohs that were Special Summoned by a Magic Card's effect
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}cannot be used as a sacrifice to tribute for another Monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He activated that Combination Effect for the mere purpose of a Tribute Summon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.35,0:06:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Monster that I'm Summoning...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out! Black Magician Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Magician Girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Master! Defeat that Evil God!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.12,0:06:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Otherwise, both of our worlds will enter a path of doom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I did not forget the promise I made back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as Doma is not defeated...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Peaceful days will not return for both this world and the Duel Monsters world!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look, Rafael!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my trump card!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Monocle of Timaeus!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.40,0:07:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... Timaeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Timaeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.74,0:07:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Combine with Black Magician Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And create a new power!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Dragon Knight Black Magician Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What was that card just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He suddenly took that card from his hand an' combined it wit' the Monster on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it. These guys got their hands on some really special cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go forth! Dragon Knight Black Magician Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Guardian Grarl!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Monster's Attack Power is lower than Guardian Grarl's!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:08:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon Knight Black Magician Girl's Special Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It calls for me to discard one card from my hand to the Graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All damage I receive is reduced to zero and the opposing Monster is destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.13,0:08:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Dragon Burst!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.27,0:08:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the power of the Legendary Dragons...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card! Self Sacrifice!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:08:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What in the world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Self Sacrifice is activated when one of my Monsters is destroyed by battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By paying 1000 Life Points, I can return the selected Monster back to the field using this card.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So my Guardian Grarl... goes unscathed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...didn't hesitate to use his own Life in exchange for his Monster's revival...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why would he go to such lengths?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nameless Pharaoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will not lose to you and your team.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know the reason behind that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because we of Doma hold a strength you guys don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A "strength" that we don't have?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.92,0:09:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The strength to accept the darkness we possess in our hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The darkness... in your hearts...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like how we have light in our hearts, we too have darkness within.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.10,0:09:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this world works like a scale - a balance acting as its foundation...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each opposite side would balance the light and darkness of our hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this would be obvious reasoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:10:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your link is with the "light in the heart,"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then us of Doma are bonded by a strong belief in the "darkness in the heart."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believing in the bonds of the darkness within your hearts...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.29,0:10:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Darkness in the heart" will forever be ahead of "light in the heart."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It lies in the deepest part of despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For people like you who pretend to be righteous all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you could never come to terms with the depth of such logic!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The depths of our despair and sorrow is unparalleled to {\i1}anyone's{\i0} on this Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.11,0:10:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That kind of thinking is wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge and destruction...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you accomplish these things, then what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd only be left with a vast emptiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do things half-heartedly, then you will most likely find only emptiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if even "emptiness" is not remaining?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.67,0:10:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you our Doma's true purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that is "nothing."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.34,0:11:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We desire to bring the history of mankind back to "zero"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're they babblin' 'bout? I can't hear a single thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you wanted to return the history of mankind to zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doma has always served as the "observers of history" from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Observers?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the first day "history" as we know it was first created, there has stood an organization behind all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's Doma!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doma has always been guiding people on their paths.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always trying to lead them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At other times, Doma would give human society a push.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, unjust methods are used just to guide history.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.28,0:12:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, humans have rebelled against Doma's ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet none of them know\N where it is they stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that, about 1000 years of history passed and people made the same mistakes over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you suppose that of all the living things on Earth, only humans are blessed with "wisdom"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because it is the fate of human beings to act as guardians and protect this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans are guardians?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In spite of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just open your eyes and look around you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the ends of this horizon, there are humans who are stained with selfish desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they are decaying this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.28,0:12:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Endlessly shedding meaningless fresh blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.74,0:12:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The foolishness of humans has gone far beyond that of Doma's expectations!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not long from now, humans will destroy this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:13:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, Doma has adjusted its aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doma has chosen to no longer guide the history of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But lead it towards the path of "reset."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean to reset the history of mankind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to decide that based on your judgment alone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not {\i1}our{\i0} judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the judgment of the lord that is of the highest ranked in Doma.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lord who manages this Earth and gave it paradise in the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person who's managed this world in the past?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nameless Pharaoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.54,0:13:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There should be "darkness" that lies dormant within the deepest thresholds of your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever thought about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of King were you in the past?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The things you have done when you obtained absolute power and authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The things... I've done...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.26,0:13:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you dare say that you were a good king?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:14:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that city was my...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.98,0:14:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I don't believe in such things!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no darkness within my heart at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should use the "light" within your heart that you believe in and {\i1}prove{\i0} it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.87,0:14:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nameless Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.58,0:14:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set two cards in reverse on my field.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I activate a Magic Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exchange?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exchange is a Magic Card that allows you to trade one card in your hand with your opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We only have one card in each of our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, we can only trade those cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.20,0:14:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Necromancy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:14:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a card that allows Monsters to be revived from your opponent's Graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.12,0:15:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have not even {\i1}one{\i0} Monster in my Graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.96,0:15:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this card has no use to you even if you hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.51,0:15:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me your card.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please accept it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi... This is your card of fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My "card of fate"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.11,0:15:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What cards did they trade?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.74,0:15:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This card is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.16,0:15:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Barrier of Orichalcos!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, you are holding a fragment of the Orichalcos you took from Gurimo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I said earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this Duel, I will not be using the The Barrier of Orichalcos.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're{\i0} the one who will be using it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:16:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should know the power of this card.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone who doesn't have a determined heart uses this card,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.31,0:16:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That person will become a prisoner in the darkness of his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.52,0:16:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But for a strong Duelist like yourself, you should be able to control it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you deny having any darkness in your heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,prove it to me by being able to control that card!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You must not use that card!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.21,0:16:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can feel the evil energy from that card...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I understand, Partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I don't use this card...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.76,0:16:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this instant, the effect of Purity of the Cemetery's Continuous Effect is activated!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have five Monsters in your Graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.43,0:16:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As such, you will be inflicted 500 points of damage to your Life Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Dragon Knight Black Magician Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Guardian Grarl once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:16:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crystal Seal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.87,0:17:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.72,0:17:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monsters that are sealed by the crystal...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only can they not attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are also unable to be sacrificed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if the trapped Monster's Attack Power changes,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this seal will be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.77,0:17:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The terrifying power of the Legendary Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as I can remove that threat entirely,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}victory will surely side with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Magician Girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.75,0:17:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will definitely save you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one Monster in face-down Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, my turn is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.47,0:17:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter what happens, he won't use the The Barrier of Orichalcos?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:17:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rod of Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rod of Silence can increase the Defense Power of a Monster equipped with this card by 500 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I activate the effect of Rod of Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can guide Guardian Kay'est onto the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guardian Grarl, destroy Yugi's Defense Position Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Swift Cleave Attack!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Shield Gardna...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My attack has not ended yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.81,0:18:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guardian Kay'est, Direct Attack Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.48,0:18:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pure Water Beam!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, I end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, I guess we will know who the victor is in the next turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.04,0:19:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not through yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right this very moment, thanks to the effects of Purity of the Cemetery,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your Life Points will fall another 600 point values!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this carries on, you will have no chance of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were unable to prove the "light" in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you will be defeated by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I... will be defeated here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised them that I'd save both our worlds...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... must not... lose in a place like this!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Magic Card, Treasure from Heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.37,0:19:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of this card's effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,both players can draw until they have six cards in their hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:19:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pointless, Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I can use this card...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dragon Knight Black Magician Girl's Attack Power would rise to 3100.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And she can be revived.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The only move that can change my predicament...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can't! Other Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.53,0:20:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can't use this card!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just {\i1}waiting{\i0} for you to use the card!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if things keep going this way, I'm bound to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner, this is {\i1}my{\i0} battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.75,0:20:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One that bets my\N way of justice and my beliefs!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other Me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to activate this card from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Barrier of Orichalcos!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.25,0:21:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Barrier of Orichalcos!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.30,0:21:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that light?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! It's Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.27,0:22:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The houses lined down the street drifting by being dyed red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.63,0:22:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I notice pain, it'll turn into happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.24,0:22:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time people wipe away tears, they understand bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.31,0:22:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warm strength that you gave me will change into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.79,0:22:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflowing feelings don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.07,0:22:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll live while I feel it, for me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.97,0:22:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Healed by overflowing friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.12,0:23:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our fated encounter is a truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.64,0:23:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday we'll be able to understand each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.12,0:23:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After being pressed into a corner,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.04,0:23:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi finally decided to use The Barrier of Orichalcos!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.54,0:23:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon Knight Black Magician Girl becomes a Dark Monster, and her Attack Points go up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.42,0:23:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which should be able to break the seal of the crystal...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.09,0:23:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Timaeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.10,0:23:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rafael was waiting for this the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.14,0:23:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you! Please don't lose, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.77,0:23:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you lose, this world will...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.02,0:23:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.19,0:23:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Darkness Within Yugi - \NTimaeus Disappears"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.15,0:23:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
